{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/PyTorch Basic/tensor-manipulation/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"HIYoung Devlog","author":"[HIYoung]","siteUrl":"https://gatsby-starter-bee.netlify.com","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"JaeYeopHan/gatsby-starter-bee"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"jbee"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"4112f4e7-76c7-59ef-a481-107d10a3cbbc","excerpt":"텐서 조작하기(Tensor Manipulation) 개요 벡터, 행렬, 텐서의 개념에 대해서 이해하고, Numpy와 PyTorch로 벡터, 행렬, 텐서를 다루는 방법에 대해서 이해한다. 벡터, 행렬 그리고 텐서(Vector, Matrix and Tensor) 딥 러닝을 위한 가장 기본적인 수학적 지식인 벡터, 행렬, 텐서에 대해서 알아볼 것이다. 넘파티 훑어보기(Numpy Review) 파이토치는 파이썬 패키지(Numpy)와 유사하다. 파이토치 텐서 선언하기(Pytorch Tensor…","html":"<ul>\n<li>\n<h1 id=\"텐서-조작하기tensor-manipulation\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%85%90%EC%84%9C-%EC%A1%B0%EC%9E%91%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0tensor-manipulation\" aria-label=\"텐서 조작하기tensor manipulation permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>텐서 조작하기(Tensor Manipulation)</h1>\n<h2 id=\"개요\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%9C%EC%9A%94\" aria-label=\"개요 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>개요</h2>\n<hr>\n<p>벡터, 행렬, 텐서의 개념에 대해서 이해하고, Numpy와 PyTorch로 벡터, 행렬, 텐서를 다루는 방법에 대해서 이해한다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>벡터, 행렬 그리고 텐서(Vector, Matrix and Tensor)</strong></p>\n<p>딥 러닝을 위한 가장 기본적인 수학적 지식인 벡터, 행렬, 텐서에 대해서 알아볼 것이다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>넘파티 훑어보기(Numpy Review)</strong></p>\n<p>파이토치는 파이썬 패키지(Numpy)와 유사하다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>파이토치 텐서 선언하기(Pytorch Tensor Allocation)</strong></p>\n<p> 파이토치 텐서 선언 방법에 대해 알아보자.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>행렬 곱셈(Matrix Multiplication)</strong></p>\n<p>행렬 연산에 대해 이해하자.</p>\n</li>\n<li><strong>다른 오퍼레이션들(Other Basic Ops)</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"1-벡터-행렬-그리고-텐서\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%EB%B2%A1%ED%84%B0-%ED%96%89%EB%A0%AC-%EA%B7%B8%EB%A6%AC%EA%B3%A0-%ED%85%90%EC%84%9C\" aria-label=\"1 벡터 행렬 그리고 텐서 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 벡터, 행렬 그리고 텐서</h2>\n<p>(Vector, Matrix and Tensor)</p>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"1-벡터-행렬-텐서-그림으로-이해하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%EB%B2%A1%ED%84%B0-%ED%96%89%EB%A0%AC-%ED%85%90%EC%84%9C-%EA%B7%B8%EB%A6%BC%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EC%9D%B4%ED%95%B4%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"1 벡터 행렬 텐서 그림으로 이해하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1) 벡터, 행렬, 텐서 그림으로 이해하기</h3>\n<p align=\"center\">\n        <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 766px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 31%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"assets 2021 09 22 00\" title=\"assets 2021 09 22 00\" src=\"/static/053b4afeee0ace0ffdb894c280a23b3d/f7616/00.png\" srcset=\"/static/053b4afeee0ace0ffdb894c280a23b3d/5a46d/00.png 300w,\n/static/053b4afeee0ace0ffdb894c280a23b3d/0a47e/00.png 600w,\n/static/053b4afeee0ace0ffdb894c280a23b3d/f7616/00.png 766w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 766px) 100vw, 766px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span>\n</p>\n<p>딥 러닝을 다룰 때에 가장 기본적인 단위는 <strong>벡터, 행렬, 텐서</strong>이다. </p>\n<ul>\n<li>차원이 없는 값을 스칼라(위의 그림에는 없음)</li>\n<li>1차원으로 구성된 값을 벡터(Vector)</li>\n<li>2차원으로 구성된 값을 행렬(Matrix)</li>\n<li>3차원 이상이 되면 텐서(Tensor)라고 부른다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>[데이터 사이언스 분야 한정으로 3차원 이상의 텐서는 그냥 다차원 행렬 또는 배열로 간주할 수 있다. 또한 주로 3차원 이상을 텐서라고 하긴 하지만, 1차원 벡터나 2차원 행렬도 텐서라고 표현하기도 한다.]</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-pytorch-tensor-shape-convention\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-pytorch-tensor-shape-convention\" aria-label=\"2 pytorch tensor shape convention permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2) Pytorch Tensor Shape Convention</h3>\n<p>딥러닝을 할 때 다루고 있는 행렬 또는 텐서의 크기를 고려하는 것은 항상 중요하다. 따라서 행렬과 텐서의 크기를 표현하는 방법을 알아보겠다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>2D Tensor(Typical Simple Setting)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>|t| = (Batch size, dim)</strong></p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 182px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"assets 2021 09 22 01\" title=\"assets 2021 09 22 01\" src=\"/static/660f0e4b7a89fe8e90df13fbcf765065/a51ee/01.png\" srcset=\"/static/660f0e4b7a89fe8e90df13fbcf765065/a51ee/01.png 182w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 182px) 100vw, 182px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span>\n</p>\n<p>위의 경우는 2차원 텐서의 크기 <strong>|t|를 (batch size x dimension)</strong>으로 표현하였을 경우이다. 아래의 그림과 같이 행렬에서 <strong>행의 크기가 batch size</strong>, <strong>열의 크기가 dim</strong>이라는 의미다.</p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 241px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 92.9460580912863%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"assets 2021 09 22 02\" title=\"assets 2021 09 22 02\" src=\"/static/9b11b1dda101ced1212838e26a24feb1/2f862/02.png\" srcset=\"/static/9b11b1dda101ced1212838e26a24feb1/2f862/02.png 241w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 241px) 100vw, 241px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span>\n</p>\n<ul>\n<li>훈련 데이터 하나의 크기가 256일 때, [6, 1, 5, …] 와 같은 배열의 길이가 256이라고 보면 된다.\n다시 말해 <strong>훈련 데이터 하나 = 벡터의 차원은 256</strong>이다.</li>\n<li>만약 이런 훈련 데이터의 개수가 3000개라고 하면 현재 훈련 데이터의 크기는 3000 x 256이다.</li>\n<li>컴퓨터는 훈련 데이터를 하나씩 처리하는 것보다 보통 <strong>덩어리로 처리</strong>하는데 <strong>64개씩 처리한다고 한다면</strong> 이 때 <strong>batch size를 64</strong>라고 한다.\n→ <strong>컴퓨터가 한 번에 처리하는 2D 텐서의 크기는 (batch size x dim) = 64 x 256이다.</strong></li>\n<li><strong>하나의 데이터의 크기= 데이터의 차원이다.\n[X] <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>t</mi><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">.</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">.</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">.</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">Data = [x] (=x_1, x_2, x_3,..., x_n)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">D</span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">a</span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">t</span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">a</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">x</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">x</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.30110799999999993em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">1</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">x</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.30110799999999993em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">x</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.30110799999999993em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">3</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">.</span><span class=\"mord\">.</span><span class=\"mord\">.</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">x</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.151392em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault mtight\">n</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span>이 아니라\n[O] <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>t</mi><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">.</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">.</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">.</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">Data = [x_1, x_2, x_3,..., x_n]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">D</span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">a</span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">t</span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">a</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">x</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.30110799999999993em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">1</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">x</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.30110799999999993em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">x</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.30110799999999993em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">3</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">.</span><span class=\"mord\">.</span><span class=\"mord\">.</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">x</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.151392em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault mtight\">n</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span></span></span></span>  이다. 따라서 n개의 차원 즉,\n하나의 데이터의 크기(n)은 데이터의 차원이라 할 수 있는 것이다.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>3D Tensor(Typical Computer Vision) - 비전 분야에서의 3차원 텐서</strong></p>\n<p>|t| = (batch size, width, height)</p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 234px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 98.71794871794873%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"assets 2021 09 22 03\" title=\"assets 2021 09 22 03\" src=\"/static/1cfe05dac1ae68347e42763eee4ea19f/7235c/03.png\" srcset=\"/static/1cfe05dac1ae68347e42763eee4ea19f/7235c/03.png 234w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 234px) 100vw, 234px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span>\n</p>\n<p><strong>비전분야(이미지, 영상 처리)</strong>를 하게 되면 좀 더 복잡한 텐서를 다루게 된다. <strong>이미지라는 것은 가로, 세로가 존재한다.</strong>\n그리고 여러 장의 이미지, 그러니까 batch size로 구성하게 되면 위와 같은 <strong>3차원의 텐서</strong>가 된다.\n위의 그림은 <strong>세로는 batch size, 가로는 너비(width), 그리고 안쪽으로는 (height)</strong>가 되는 것을 볼 수 있다. </p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>3D Tensor(Typical Natural Language Processing) - NLP 분야에서의 3차원 텐서</strong></p>\n<p>|t| = (batch size, length, dim)자연어 처리는 보통 (batch size, 문장 길이, 단어 벡터의 차원)이라는 3차원 텐서를 사용한다.</p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 239px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 95.81589958158995%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"assets 2021 09 22 04\" title=\"assets 2021 09 22 04\" src=\"/static/df89d322fe892034fcc40401eefb88a3/4a279/04.png\" srcset=\"/static/df89d322fe892034fcc40401eefb88a3/4a279/04.png 239w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 239px) 100vw, 239px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span>\n</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>NLP 분야의 3D 텐서 예재로 이해하기</strong></p>\n<p>아래와 같이 4개의 문장으로 구성된 전체 훈련 데이터가 있다하자.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>나는 사과를 좋아해<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>나는 바나나를 좋아해<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>나는 사과를 싫어해<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>나는 바나나를 싫어해<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>컴퓨터는 다음과 같이 데이터를 입력받았을 때에 ‘나는 사과를 좋아해’가 단어가 1개인지 3개인지 이해하지 못하기에 단어별로 나눠줘야한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'나는'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'사과를'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'좋아해'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'나는'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'바나나를'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'좋아해'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'나는'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'사과를'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'싫어해'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'나는'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'바나나를'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'싫어해'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이제 훈련 데이터의 크기는 4 x 3의 크기를 가지는 2D 텐서이다. 컴퓨터는 텍스트보다 숫자를 더 잘 처리할 수 있기에 각 단어를 벡터로 만들 것이다.  아래의 기준을 통해 단어를 3차원의 벡터로 변환했다 해보자.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token string\">'나는'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.9</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">'사과를'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">'바나나를'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">'좋아해'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">'싫어해'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.9</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.9</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.9</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.9</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이제 훈련 데이터는 4 x 3 x 3의 크기를 가지는 3D 텐서이다. 이제 batch size를 2로 해보겠다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">첫번째 배치 <span class=\"token comment\">#1</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.9</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.9</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n\n두번째 배치 <span class=\"token comment\">#2</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.9</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.9</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>컴퓨터는 배치 단위로 가져가서 연산을 수행한다. 각 배치의 텐서의 크기는 2 x 3 x 3이다. 이는 (batch size, 문장 길이, 단어 벡터의 차원)의 크기이다. </p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"텐서 다루기","date":"September 22, 2021"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/PyTorch Basic/tensor-manipulation/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/PyTorch Basic/basic-componets-of-pytorch-package/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"파이토치 패키지의 기본구성"}},"next":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["2486386679","3128451518"]}